thread.title: Jarek Tabor

author: Jarek Tabor
title: Jarek Tabor
text: One of the few companies, which actually processes the orders quickly and delivers quickly after placing the order. Good information on stock availability of the products. Good selection of the accesories, splited per compatibility. Comfortable payment methods, suitable for anyone, from invoice by Klarna, Klarna Direkt, card payments, direct bank payment. No Paypal though.
